Keith White
Director

Principal owner of Marketplace Home Mortgage, LLC (“MHM”), a full service correspondence residential mortgage lender
Owns and manages Alliance Title, LLC, Marketplace Insurance Services and various commercial office buildings
Founded Marketline Constructions Capital, LLC, a construction lender, and founded Maribella Mortgage, LLC, a wholesale mortgage lender
Worked as the Minnesota-Wisconsin Area Manager with GMAC Mortgage
Undergraduate degree from St. Cloud State University with a major in finance, real estate and economics



